episodes.title: Identity Formation after Leaving Strict Religion. Claire Ashman Podcast April 2023
episodes.description:
Assistant Professor Schneur Zalman Newfield and I discuss the lack of socialisation within insulated religious groups and how that affects exiters when they are adjusting to living in the outside world.




You can read more at www.ZalmanNewfield.com




More about Claire Ashman at www.claireashman.com
